FBIS3-23130 "jptot010__l94093" JPRS-TOT-94-010-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 10 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ISRAEL Update on, Reactions to Hebron Mosque Massacre Police To Seize `Extremists' Automatic Weapons TA2802165494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1600 GMT 28 Feb 94 TA2802165494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] The police minister has ordered the confiscation of the automatic weapons of extremist settlers in Judaea and Samaria, but let them keep their personal weapons, such as guns. He also ordered the police commissioner to release all the Israeli Arabs who were arrested during demonstrations in the last few days if they are not suspected of having hit policemen or damaged property.
